Enable the feature: 

​1. ​ Settings → Apps → Optional features → More Windows features 

​2. ​ Check Windows Sandbox → OK → Restart



Launch Sandbox: ​

● ​ Search for “Windows Sandbox” in Start menu 

​● ​ Or run: Start-Process "WindowsSandbox.exe"






Sandbox supports configuration files (.wsb) that allow fine-grained control over each session. Create an XML file with .wsb extension and double-click to launch customized Sandbox.

